{"type": "article", "id": 63887, "title": "王源代言中华牙膏，宜家动画短片挺可爱 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-05-20T05:28:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7217, "name": "周年"}, {"id": 8573, "name": "服务"}, {"id": 475, "name": "QQ"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190520122207nqFlS0MTrfH85WAN.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"crdT\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/7018619499/4373570824428582\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Tom Ford 美妆宣布刘昊然和景甜分别为中国区品牌彩妆大使和中国区品牌香氛形象大使，</b></a>去年年底它在上海开设了首家美妆精品店。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190520122542VtonITPJFC9316Xi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190520122542gqKG5OAHh40mF2nW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.377778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"VGqj\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1800861037/4373618118764238\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>王源成为中华牙膏品牌代言人，</b></a>他最近刚代言乐事和馥蕾诗。之前品牌代言人是刘昊然。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190520122605iskreIvfjnTEP4aV.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"vhB6\" class=\"\"></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4373739145338736?sourceType=weixin&amp;wm=9006_2001&amp;featurecode=newtitle&amp;from=timeline&amp;isappinstalled=0\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">聚划算和宝洁合作，推出“迪士尼 11 公主成团”活动。</a>参与者从 14 位公主中选出 11 位组成女团生成海报，结果导向推出的公主礼盒套装页面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190520132245yYPGnZLq0IAep9JR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.283986\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190520132245MAZnk9mR2iWg41Vv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.828000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190520132245ZS8y4BRNolEOK2VY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.828000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190520132246Blf7Fs8cVuOMA9I1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.828000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=r0872oeon9s\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"vhB6\"><b><a href=\"https://actqzs.qzone.qq.com/external/6b5d58cf6136dd2735d67ec1c3e14a14/index.html?_wv=1&amp;g_f=&amp;srctype=&amp;ticket=\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">QQ 发布 20周年品牌广告片《时光密码》。</a></b>QQ 借 520 之际，故事讲了一对夫妻通过 QQ 网恋到步入婚姻，感情出现危机的同时丈夫也忘记了当年使用的 QQ 密码，最终靠重温第一次网友见面解决了问题。故事安排的有点刻意。此外，导演是张大鹏。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=f08719wqfd0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"xpWR\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ny-MGNf301k&amp;feature=youtu.be\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" savefrom_lm_index=\"0\" savefrom_lm=\"1\"><b>苹果拍了支音乐人主题广告片 <em>Behind the Music. Behind the Mac。</em></b></a><span style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; margin-left: 5px;\"><a href=\"http://savefrom.net/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNy-MGNf301k%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&amp;utm_source=chameleon&amp;utm_medium=extensions&amp;utm_campaign=link_modifier\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Get a direct link\" savefrom_lm=\"1\" savefrom_lm_is_link=\"1\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;data:image/gif;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; width: 16px; height: 16px; display: inline-block; border: none; text-decoration: none; padding: 0px; position: relative;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a></span>5、6 月，英国音乐节季来临，苹果和代理商 TBWA 媒体艺术实验室将镜头对准音乐创作者的技术设备 Mac 上。片中既有音乐巨星保罗·麦卡唐尼、大卫·鲍伊，也有新兴音乐人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=m0872g299p6\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"WcX5\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/jxF6AnlY6GE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" savefrom_lm_index=\"0\" savefrom_lm=\"1\"><b>百威新品牌 campaign “Be a King” ，聚焦在韩国非法职业文身师身上。</b></a><span style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; margin-left: 5px;\"><a href=\"http://savefrom.net/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjxF6AnlY6GE&amp;utm_source=chameleon&amp;utm_medium=extensions&amp;utm_campaign=link_modifier\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Get a direct link\" savefrom_lm=\"1\" savefrom_lm_is_link=\"1\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;data:image/gif;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; width: 16px; height: 16px; display: inline-block; border: none; text-decoration: none; padding: 0px; position: relative;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a></span>一系列短片、海报和艺术展览以及限量版包装啤酒，都是为了让文身师职业合法化，希望这一职业得到认同。创意代理商是 Virtue。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u08720ocykb\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"WgqN\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/RkYQQK-w2Lg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" savefrom_lm_index=\"0\" savefrom_lm=\"1\"><b>YouTube 展示了三位普通澳大利亚人的故事。</b></a><span style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; margin-left: 5px;\"><a href=\"http://savefrom.net/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRkYQQK-w2Lg&amp;utm_source=chameleon&amp;utm_medium=extensions&amp;utm_campaign=link_modifier\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Get a direct link\" savefrom_lm=\"1\" savefrom_lm_is_link=\"1\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;data:image/gif;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; width: 16px; height: 16px; display: inline-block; border: none; text-decoration: none; padding: 0px; position: relative;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a></span>Charles Lomu，MacinleyButson 和 Eddie Woo 把 YouTube 作为学习和教育平台，分享内容产生了不小的影响。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=i0872qoox28\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u08722ung2g\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"wi4N\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kgjQmIt17-Y\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" savefrom_lm_index=\"0\" savefrom_lm=\"1\"><b>宜家新活动 “We Love the Things You Hate”（我们喜欢你讨厌的事情）展示了它的便捷服务。</b></a><span style=\"padding: 0; margin: 0; margin-left: 5px;\"><a href=\"http://savefrom.net/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkgjQmIt17-Y&amp;utm_source=chameleon&amp;utm_medium=extensions&amp;utm_campaign=link_modifier\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Get a direct link\" savefrom_lm=\"1\" savefrom_lm_is_link=\"1\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;data:image/gif;base64,&quot;); background-repeat: no-repeat; width: 16px; height: 16px; display: inline-block; border: none; text-decoration: none; padding: 0px; position: relative;\" rel=\"nofollow\"></a></span>四支简短可爱的动画呈现了遇到不愉快的体验，宜家可以提供组装家具、送货到家等服务。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d087220uxeb\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=u0872mn1lp1\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=w08727483f3\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"iGxE\"><a href=\"http:// https://www.wsj.com/articles/google-to-refund-advertisers-after-suit-over-fraud-scheme-11558113251\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google 计划退还因欺诈产生的 7500 万美元广告预算。</b></a>2017 年广告主向 Google 购买广告后，发现网站流量是机器人点击程序诞生的。另外在线广告公司 Ad TraderI nc. 起诉 Google 后，提到部分虚假流量导向了后者完全控制的 AdX 和 AdSense。</p><p line=\"AwMr\"><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/advertisers-pack-into-u-k-game-of-thrones-finale-11558117162\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>《权游》最终季吸引了美国品牌之外的大量广告主。</b></a>因为 HBO 不播广告，英国品牌广告主可以在付费电视频道 Sky Atlantic 上投放广告。《权游》每 30 秒广告本季平均价格约为 63980 美元，不过在大结局中价格又大幅攀升。</p><p line=\"u9MM\">题图来自：宜家</p>"}